        {
            "id": 6008108,
            "title": "東科-KY 5月營收7.98億元年月雙減 強調台幣升值僅報表影響無匯損",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東科 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5225:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5225\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5225-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收為 7.98 億元，呈年月雙減；累計前 5 月營收 44.3 億元，較去年同期減少 8.03%；東科 - KY 表示，帳面損失純粹為報表呈現美元轉為<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>差異，故無<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>匯兌損失。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008108%2Fl%2F8937f90738de554f571fd82802d9d30c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">東科-KY 5月營收7.98億元年月雙減 強調台幣升值僅報表影響無匯損。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東科 - KY 5 月營收 7.98 億元，月減 15.2%、年減 20.2%；累計前 5 月營收 44.3 億元，較去年同期減少 8.03%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東科 - KY 表示，公司並無美元兌換為<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>之營收，交易貨幣除少數廠區所在地內銷之<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>及越南盾外，全數為美元，而公司以報表表達貨幣 - <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>換算營收公告，因<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>升值而以<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>列示金額與前期或去年同期而減少。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東科 - KY 提到，因美元營收並無實際兌換成<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>，故損益表內並無交易類<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>匯兌損失，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>升值對營運並無重大影響， 營運展望仍視關稅塵埃落定後明朗。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
